Goal of Project
========================================================

The goal of the project is to create Shiny application and
present it through Slidify application.

Shiny Application
========================================================

The application converts an entered degree in Fahrenheit between
-100 to 1000 to the degrees in Kelvin and celsius.

The application may be accessed at the following URL-

https://hanjookim.shinyapps.io/project

