Underlying Code
========================================================

The following is the portion of the code that coverts
the degrees.

Fahrenheit to Kevin   <- function(FtoK) ((FtoK - 32) * (5/9)) + 273.15
Fahrenheit to Celsius <- function(FtoC) ((FtoC - 32) * (5/9))
